These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, domino, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing domino##1
2. the person playing poker is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing domino##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Game   | scrabble | poker | domino |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, dog, chinchilla
1. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the chinchilla##2
2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Pet   | chinchilla | goat | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, manager, freelancer
1. the manager is between the videographer and the freelancer##2
2. the manager is on the left of the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Job   | freelancer | manager | videographer |

 #################################

 
