.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, skiing, rugby
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is skiing##2
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Sport   | skiing | volleyball | rugby |

